  <acceptance-criteria>
    <criterion testable="true">`src/client/shared/Spaarke.AI.Widgets/src/widgets/context/FilePreviewContextWidget.tsx` exists, exports a default `ContextWidgetComponent&lt;FilePreviewContextData&gt;`, and compiles cleanly under the project's TS config (strict mode).</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Single-file mode (`files.length === 1`) renders inline preview using the extracted `RichFilePreview` renderer (task 013) — verified by inspecting imports (NO local re-implementation of iframe / metadata / prev-next UI).</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Multi-file mode (`files.length &gt; 1`) renders a vertical Fluent v9 card list above the active preview; clicking a card swaps the active preview AND dispatches `context.file_selected` with `{ fileId, fileName }` payload (additive event type from task 016).</criterion>
